channel.title: Deob 377 - Receive packet 76
channel.description:
In deob 377 you can find receiving packet 76, this is the welcome screen for 377. I managed to send the values to the client in a correct way, but the welcome screen does not open.
Anyone got any solutions for this?
Someone already told me it COULD be the cache, but i doubt that...
